&lt;/h3>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.wuko.top/posts/2024/10/30/newbiectf.html/misc2.png"
width="1860"
height="1798"
srcset="https://blog.wuko.top/posts/2024/10/30/newbiectf.html/misc2_hu9439625977773339056.png 480w, https://blog.wuko.top/posts/2024/10/30/newbiectf.html/misc2_hu18167751659464539628.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="misc2"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="103"
data-flex-basis="248px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>提示：这不只是个图片&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;code>WinHEX&lt;/code>查看16进制，发现里面有zip的头尾：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ZIP
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">50 4B 03 04
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">50 4B 05 06
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;code>binwalk&lt;/code>提取出压缩包，解压得到第二张图片，扫码得到flag：&lt;/p>
